General.Name: Censof Holdings Bhd
General.Description: Censof Holdings Berhad, an investment holding company, engages in the design, development, implementation, and marketing of financial management software and related services primarily in Malaysia, Singapore, and Indonesia. The company operates through four segments: Financial Management Solutions, Corporate Services, Wealth Management Solutions, and Digital Technology. It also provides services for financial applications, electronic payments, and collections solutions; and services for portfolio management, fund accounting, unit registry, selling agent, and online transactions. In addition, the company offers computer programming, consultancy, and related services; services for software development for financial applications, electronics payments, and wealth management applications; software as a service; and enterprise resource planning software. Further, it is involved in the computer consultancy, computer facilities management, and other information technology services activities; and business of trading in business software; sale of computerized accounting systems. Additionally, the company provides information technology consultancy and services for system integration, cloud-based solutions, e-procurement, e-tendering, and other related services. It serves government agencies, large corporations, and small and medium enterprises (SMEs), as well as micro-SMEs. The company was formerly known as Century Software Holdings Berhad. Censof Holdings Berhad was incorporated in 2008 and is headquartered in Petaling Jaya, Malaysia.
